-- Richemont’s Baume & Mercier CEO Sees Rising Sales, Le Temps Says
-- B y   S i m e o n   B e n n e t t
-- 2012-05-01T12:51:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-01/richemont-s-baume-mercier-ceo-sees-rising-sales-le-temps-says.html
Baume & Mercier, a watchmaking unit of
 Cie. Financiere Richemont SA (CFR) , said its sales are showing “very
strong growth,” Le Temps  reported , citing an interview with
Alain Zimmermann, Baume & Mercier’s chief executive officer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
